{"tid":1154837,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"1988變1998《請回答1988》傳拍中國版 變《相約九八》","createTime":"2019-05-14T14:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T06:01:53.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"127971efcff66a937fea777b87aea9bf89cb1145","tid":1154837,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190514/photo/bkn-20190514210034841-0514_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190514210047\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190514%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190514210034841-0514_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190514210047&h=06e7d362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由韓星柳俊烈、朴寶劍、高庚杓及女團Girl's Day成員惠利主演的tvN電視台人氣韓劇《請回答1988》，今日傳出將翻拍中國版，根據國家新聞出版廣電總局的4月電視劇備案顯示，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大熱韓劇《請回答1988》將被騰訊影業翻拍，劇集改名為《相約九八》。</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1611/e1611544.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1611%2Fe1611544.jpg&h=29ba25bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《請回答<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1988</span></strong>》講述1988年住在首爾市道峰區雙門洞的五個家庭的故事，描述溫暖的親情、鄰里街坊小市民的故事、傳統的愛情與友情，而中國版的故事設定為在1997年香港回歸前後的深圳羅湖區，講述同住在某條小街的五戶人家的故事，神經大條又可愛細心的李文靜，將在高冷的黃淼和內斂的徐濤中作出決擇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係味1988太近1989<br />\nENDING唔知點改<br />\n要變做1998<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8657732f8cf2d65ad106ebb652eb81440723b3c8","tid":1154837,"uid":117802,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:14:40.000Z","msg":"請回應 1989 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ff54a4dbec13ed94bee98a15be5d4b9a93d740","tid":1154837,"uid":64476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:15:17.000Z","msg":"係都拍1989啦"},{"pid":"496f64bbe266cec66b80abed7937be1bf539981d","tid":115